{"tid":1656623,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］有咩方法確保水彈唔會爆到自己？","createTime":"2019-10-15T16:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T14:39:28.000Z","uid":25846,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"22619f26a18d7385dc811972d630534509435475","tid":1656623,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:27:31.000Z","msg":"小弟最近同朋友玩ocamp黎緊會玩水game <br />\n你知啦水彈梗係要掉中對家先興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但玩個時怕會太肉緊揸爆水彈，整濕自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁有冇咩方法確保我可以成功掉到出去<br />\n有距離之餘又唔怕整濕自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申玩ocamp 對面隊好撚串<br />\n想整濕哂佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810e38d8699d32de857352b8525c1cd819d7c4b6","tid":1656623,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:27:41.000Z","msg":"「突發」大量民陣1020九龍大遊行文宣流出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1655703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1655703</a>"},{"pid":"f67702f54893a6470d9567a27622e7de1420ef3e","tid":1656623,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:28:02.000Z","msg":"高處得唔得呀"},{"pid":"a95df07f86a7a4ff57b6acde1d703385d2254eca","tid":1656623,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:29:08.000Z","msg":"一見到Ocamp就下意識負評咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ca74c6d97e81d050902256de62a6da3d83da69","tid":1656623,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:30:24.000Z","msg":"買個大口水樽裝住<br />\n要掟先拎出黎"},{"pid":"07433d0ae6ef2810b9e10c2ea7dc7c0464a0d3da","tid":1656623,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a95df07f86a7a4ff57b6acde1d703385d2254eca","tid":1656623,"uid":30836,"like":